OL,3,CBody found in search for missing boy,
OL,4,C15, in lake
OL,6,FPolice have found a body in the search
OL,7,Ffor a 15-year-old swimmer who had gone
OL,8,Fmissing in a lake at a Hampshire
OL,9,Fnature reserve.
OL,11,FThe Emergency Services were called to
OL,12,Fthe scene at Testwood Lakes near
OL,13,FTotton, Southampton on Wednesday 24
OL,14,FJune 2026.
OL,16,FOfficers had received a report that a
OL,17,Fboy had gone missing after being seen
OL,18,Fswimming in the water
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/3
