OL,3,CBody found in search for missing boy,
OL,4,C15, in lake
OL,6,FIn a statement, a spokesperson for
OL,7,FHampshire Police said: " Officers
OL,8,Fsearching for a missing 15-year-old
OL,9,Fboy who was last seen swimming in
OL,10,Fwater at Testwood Lakes, including
OL,11,Fthose from our Marine Unit, have sadly
OL,12,Fnow located a body.
OL,14,F"The boy's family have been informed,
OL,15,Fand formal identification has taken
OL,16,Fplace.
OL,18,F"His family are being supported by
OL,19,Fspecially trained officers.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/3
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
