OL,3,CBody found in search for missing boy,
OL,4,C15, in lake
OL,6,F"A file will be prepared for the
OL,7,Fcoroner"
OL,9,FA multi-agency operation was launched
OL,10,Fto find a missing 15-year-old boy.
OL,12,FHampshire Police marine units, the
OL,13,FNational Police Air Service, South
OL,14,FCentral Ambulance Service and
OL,15,FHampshire & Isle of Wight Fire Service
OL,16,Fwere involved in the search.
